comments: Belinelli (SAS) is moving alongside Lowry's (TOR) path and maintains a legal guarding position as he defends the drive.
Aldridge (SAS) is already in Powell's (TOR) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Ibaka (TOR) makes marginal contact with White (SAS) at the end of his drive.
Ibaka (TOR) briefly grasps Aldridge's (SAS) jersey during rebounding.
DeRozan (SAS) is moving alongside Lowry's (TOR) path and maintains a legal guarding position as he defends the drive.
Anunoby (TOR) is moving alongside DeRozan's (SAS) path to the basket and maintains a legal guarding position as he defends the drive.
Anunoby (TOR) legally contests DeRozan's (SAS) jump shot attempt.
White (SAS) moves laterally into Lowry's (TOR) path and affects his SQBR.
DeRozan (TOR) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Siakam (TOR) in the post.
DeRozan (SAS) does not maintain legal guarding position and makes contact to Siakam's (TOR) arm that affects his shot attempt.
Aldridge (SAS) is already in Anunoby's (TOR) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Lowry (TOR) makes marginal contact with DeRozan (SAS) during his drive.
Anunoby (TOR) is already in Aldridge's (SAS) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
DeRozan (SAS) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Siakam (TOR) in the post.
Ibaka (TOR) and Walker IV (SAS) briefly engage and disengage during rebounding.
Anunoby (TOR) makes incidental contact with Walker IV (SAS) as he attempts to secure the ball.
DeRozan (SAS) advances the ball into the frontcourt within eight seconds.
Lowry (TOR) jumps A to B into DeRozan (SAS) and affects his driving shot attempt.
DeRozan (SAS) legally contests Lowry's (TOR) jump shot attempt.
Lowry (TOR) briefly grasps DeRozan's (SAS) arm, but does not affect his FOM during the inbound.
Anunoby (TOR) commits a take foul on Aldridge (SAS).
DeRozan (SAS) trips over his teammate's foot and goes to the floor as a result of this contact, not as a result of any contact from Siakam (TOR).
Walker IV (SAS) legally contests Siakam's (TOR) jump shot attempt.
